    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade specimen of the legendary E46 M3, finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example features the celebrated S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by six individual throttle bodies. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift throws, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. Mechanically flawless, the high-pressure VANOS system has been proactively serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure peak chassis rigidity. Suspension dynamics remain taut with zero bushing deflection, and the factory-spec forged Style 67 wheels are wrapped in fresh Michelin Pilot Sport 4S rubber. This is a turn-key, investment-grade driver\u2019s car with a documented service history and pristine aesthetics.",
      "price": 48500.0,
