      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, rock chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats are supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It comes with a comprehensive, documented service history with all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships. There are no leaks, no undercarriage corrosion, and the engine delivers smooth, effortless power while the transmission shifts with surgical precision. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle with a clean title and no accident history. It drives, smells, and looks like a brand-new car. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise, this vehicle stands in a class of its own.",
